David Grimal are o cariera internationala ca violinist solo, Peter Csaba, Heinrich Schiff, Heinrich Schiff, Emmanuel Krivine, Mikhail Pletnev, Rafael Fruhehbeck de Burgos si Peter Eotvos, Andris Philharmonique de Radio France, Orchestra Nationala de Camera de Comert a Frantei, Berliner Symphoniker, New Japan Philharmonic, Orchestre de l 'Opera de Lyon, Salzburg Mozarteum Orchestra, Jerusalem Symphony Orchestra si Sinfonia Varsovia sub bagheta unor conducatoare precum: Orchestra Nationala de Camera Radio, Orchestra Nationala Philharmonique de Camera Nationala de Camera de Camera de Camera a Rusiei, Berliner Symphonium, Sinfonia de Camera Nationala de Camera de Camera de Camera, Orchestra de camera si Sinfonia Philharmonique de Radio, Orchestra Nationala de Camera Nationala de Camera Nationala de Camera Radio, Berliner Symphoniker, Orchestra de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera de Camera.
Cateva lucrari i-au fost dedicate acestuia de catre cativa composeri, printre care Marc-Andre Dalbavie, Brice Pauset, Thierry Escaich, Jean-Francois Zygel, Alexander Gasparov, Victor Kissine, Fuminori Tanada, Richard Dubugnon, Ivan Fedele, Philippe Harrowing, Anders Hillborg, Oscar Bianchi, Guillaume Connesson si Frederic Verrieres.
